    <releaseNotes>
    - New: A new 'cover grid' view of the books in your calibre library
    - New: A new, faster database backend
    - New: RTF Input: Add option to ignore WMF images iinstead of replacing them with a placeholder.
	- New: Content server: Make virtual libraries available as searches from the start page. They work just like saved searches, clicking on a virtual library will show you all the books in that virtual library.
    - Fixed: Remove extra, useless 'language' entry in metadata download configuration dialog
    - Fixed: Kobo driver: Display device collections even if the driver is configured to not manage shelves on the device.
	- Fixed: Fix typo in calibre.desktop file on linux
	- Fixed: Edit metadata dialog: Disable OK button while results are being downloaded.
	- Fixed: In OS X 10.8 Apple stopped redirecting stdout/stderr to Console.app for applications launched by launch services. Re-enable the redirection, useful for debugging.
	- Fixed: Fix virtual library tabs not being updated when using VL button
	- New News Source: News24 and Nuus24 by Nicki de Wet
    - Improved News Source: Consumerist
	- Improved News Source: jeuxvideo
	- Improved News Source: Metro UK
	- Improved News Source: El Tribuno
	- Improved News Source: High Country News
	- Improved News Source: Daily Express
	- Improved News Source: Providence Journal
	- Improved News Source: mediapart
    </releaseNotes>
